            "reviews": "“It's like action-FTL meets Legos.”<br><a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=mBIZJUIim_s\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noreferrer\"  >Retromation</a><br><br>“...improvisational, gleeful and brutal. Swish, stately overhaul of an already top-notch DIY arcade create ‘em up, with more structure and customization options than the original.”<br><a href=\"http://www.pcgamer.com/captain-forever-remix-review-early-access/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noreferrer\"  >PC Gamer</a><br><br>“It might be the arcade roguelikelike to help stop The Binding of Isaac: Rebirth dominating my thoughts.”<br><a href=\"http://www.rockpapershotgun.com/2015/03/28/build-shoot-loot-build-captain-forever-remix-released/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noreferrer\"  >Rock Paper Shotgun</a><br>",
